Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper focuses on improving image classification and object detection/segmentation, which are core topics in computer vision.
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The proposed Linear Context Transform (LCT) block is a machine learning module that implicitly captures dependencies between channels and linearly transforms the global context of each channel.
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a new module that improves the performance of deep learning models, which is a key area of research in artificial intelligence.
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper proposes a lightweight module that improves the performance of deep learning models, which is a key area of research in neural networks.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper focuses on improving image classification and object detection/segmentation, which are important applications of multimedia analysis.
